{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"7":"Fasting"},"section_detail":{"7":{"hadithnumber_first":1638,"hadithnumber_last":1782,"arabicnumber_first":1638,"arabicnumber_last":1782}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1669,"arabicnumber":1669,"text":"Rapporté par Abu Salamah : J’ai entendu ‘Aishah dire : « J’avais des jours de jeûne à rattraper du mois de Ramadan, et je ne les rattrapais qu’à l’arrivée de Sha’ban. »","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Hasan Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih - Bukhari And Muslim"}],"reference":{"book":7,"hadith":32}}]}